      "title": "Selfie craze claims another life; youth falls from waterfall",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "A young man fell into a waterfall at Udaveriya Estate in \u200b\u200bHaldummulla while taking a selfie yesterday.",
        "Police said two young men visited the waterfall and one of them slipped and fell into the waterfall while going to take a selfie.",
        "The dead body of the victim was found about 200 meters below of the waterfall."
